<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-01-27 01:14 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7820 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u s BC-BKN-CELTICSMAGIC-BOS &LR;      01-27 0722
