   BELLOW-NOVEL (Undated) _ By the time they reach their 80s most
great writers have long ceased their creative output, but this
April in his eighty fifth year, the Nobel prize winning author Saul
Bellow is set to publish his first major novel in over a decade. By
Dinitia Smith.
</P>
