<P>
   TLC-FUTURE _ ATLANTA _ A look at the future of TLC and its
members (they have a show on Super Bowl eve in Atlanta). The trio
talks about the spatting they've been doing in some magazines and
where their heads are now that the holidays are over. They make
beautiful music together, but only Lisa ``Left-Eye'' Lopes wants a
music career. Tionne ``T-Boz'' Watkins wants to make movies.
Rozonda ``Chilli'' Thomas just wants to make babies. (SoMurray,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 40.
</P>
