   ARTS-ATLANTA _ ATLANTA _ As he gets ready to leave town after
nine years of directing the High Museum of Art, Ned Rifkin says
Atlanta's corporations simply have to raise the bar when supporting
the arts if the city hopes to achieve significant cultural status.
A Q&AMP;A. (TSabulis, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 45. WITH PHOTO.
</P>
