trick is how to reduce the odds. Here's a checklist of precautions
from consumer advocate Clark Howard and from a useful State
Department publication called ``A Safe Trip Abroad.'' (Auchmutey,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution). WITH ILLUSTRATION. ed for
extensively) or the bodacious bod of Barbie (for whom he also
creates out-of-this-world looks), they can make you feel pretty
darn close to princess-like. The 60-year-old designer recently
