   FBN-RAMS-WHITE (Atlanta) _ Semantically speaking, there's a
difference between being bitter and being bitterly disappointed.
That difference defines Mike White, who was fired after two seasons
as head coach of the Oakland Raiders but is now assistant head
coach of a Super Bowl-bound team with the St. Louis Rams. By JOHN
CRUMPACKER.
