<P>
   &UR; FROM IDAHO TO ISRAEL, U.S. ELECTION WILL AFFECT EVERYONE &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   (ATTN: Political, Commentary Editors) &QL;
</P>
<P>
   (Moved Jan. 25 to ``a,'' ``p,'' and ``k'' news files) &QL;
</P>
<P>
   (500 words) &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; BY RUPERT CORNWELL, The Independent of London &LR;  &QL;
