<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-01-27 13:58 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8131 &Cx1f; ttj-z
r d BC-FLU-FIGHTERS-2TAKES-H     01-27 1275
