   With photo.
</P>
<P>
   CLINTON-SKETCH (Washington) _ Clinton's first State of the Union
in two years not under the shadow of Monica, as Hillary in the
stands, and Al, standing behind him, eye jobs they hope will soon
be theirs. By Lizette Alvarez.
</P>
