<P>
   &UR; COMPUTERS (a) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   HOLY-DOTCOM (Undated) _ Beliefnet.com is the first website to
attempt to encompass all of the world's principal religions and
belief systems. It's an ambitious site with a slick mix of news and
advice. By William A. Davis. 1500 words.
</P>
<P>
   COMPUTERS-CYBERSPACE (Undated) -- The way Dennis Fong sees it,
games are the final frontier of cyberspace, the future of the
entertainment business. By Patti Hartigan. 1390 words.
