<P>
   STATE OF THE UNION SPEECH
</P>
<P>
   UNION _ WASHINGTON _ President Clinton delivers his final State
of the Union address Thursday night. (Deans, Cox News Service). 30.
</P>
<P>
   WITH
</P>
<P>
   UNION-GORE _ (Will have a New Hampshire dateline) _ How Vice
President Al Gore fared politically in President Clinton's State of
the Union speech. (Shepard, Cox News Service). 12.
</P>
<P>
