   PAKISTAN-U.S. (Washington) _ The United States warned Pakistan
on Thursday that it could be branded a sponsor of terrorism _
making it ineligible for virtually all U.S. aid _ if it gave direct
support to a terrorist group that operates in Kashmir. (Summary
from wires) By Philip Shenon.
