<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-01-27 17:25 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8398 &Cx1f; tth-z
r e BC-TV-COMMON-SPI &LR;      01-27 0714
