gorilla? Any way he wants. Lots of good details on the illness and
treatment of the famed Atlanta Zoo gorilla Willie B, including
costs, details on how the vets get to him, etc. (Hulbert, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 30. WITH PHOTOS.
