<P>
   CAMPAIGN-BUSH (Nashua, N.H.) _ Governor George W. Bush insists
he will win the N.H. primary. But as polls show him trailing
Senator John S. McCain, it seems Bush's mind is already someplace
else. By Ann E. Kornblut and Jill Zuckman. 1200 words.
</P>
