Rican officials meet to discuss permanently closing the Navy's
bombing range on the island of Vieques, Sila Calderon, San Juan's
mayor, blasts the service for its ``appalling'' and ``shameful''
treatment of the island's 9,000 residents. By ERIC ROSENBERG.
(Already filed.)
