his attack on Vice President Al Gore for ``misrepresenting'' his
policy proposals and insists that a candidate must speak the truth
on the campaign trail. Bradley _ who has previously criticized the
vice president for misrepresenting his health plan _ says if a
candidate does not tell the truth in the campaign, the American
people can't trust him to tell the truth as president. By STEWART
M. POWELL. (Already filed.)
