<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-01-27 20:59 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8691 &Cx1f; taf-z
u w BC-CLINTON-ECONOMY-NYT &LR;      01-27 1036
