</P>
<P>
   (NYT31) WASHINGTON -- Jan. 27, 2000 -- CLINTON-SPEECH-1 --
President Clinton greets the audience at his final State of the
Union speech while Vice President Al Gore and House Speaker Dennis
Hastert look on. With one eye on his own legacy and another on the
political aspirations of his vice president, Clinton claimed credit
Thursday night for leading the nation onto the broad uplands of
unparalleled prosperity and laid out an election-year manifesto for
